data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS UPDATES!!  Welcome to this charming, colonial style home in the heart of Fort Walton Beach. This home is located near schools, shopping, and just a short drive to Eglin AFB and the local beaches. This is the perfect starter home for a growing family or will make an excellent rental property for your growing rental portfolio. Please call James Ruckel today to schedule your private showing.
